            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De lucri acquisitionis honestate consideranda</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
      ¶ De lucri acquisitionis honestate
      <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>consideranda. Rubrica. 4
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e118">PSalmista. 36 psalamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e125">
               Me<lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>lius est 
               mo<lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>dicum iusto super diuitias 
               peccato<lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>rum multas.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e134">Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e139">Melius est
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>parum cum iusticia quam multi fructus cum 
               ini<lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>quitate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e148">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e147">c. 17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e150">Melior est bucella sicca cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>gaudio quam domus plena victimis cum iurgio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e159">Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. 2 ad fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e160">Amplectere magis iustam penuriam quam 
               in<lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>iustas diuitias. haec enim iustitia diuitiis 
               poti<lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>or. Neminem celeris lucrantem nequiter.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e175">Aristotelis pollyticorum: lib. 6. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e174">Multi
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>magis appetunt lucrum quam honorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e187">Iesus filius sirach. in ecclesiast. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e184">Noli
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>anxius esse in diuitiis iniustis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e190">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e197">13. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e192">
               Bo<lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>na est substantia cui non est peccatum in conscientia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>
                / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e209">31. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e202">Beatus diues qui inuentus est sine
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>macula.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e222">Terentius in adelphis.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e213">Pecuniam in 
               lo<lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>co negligere maximum interdum est lucrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e234">Tullius retho. artis noue: li 6. et fi. c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e223">Due res sunt que possunt homines ad 
               tur<lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>pe compendium promouere: inopia: atque
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>auaritia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e250">Cassiodorus epistolarum: li. 5. c. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e237">
               Pul<lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>chrum est commodum feda neglexisse lucra
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>pecunie.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e245">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e262">Li. 8. e. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e247">Pecunias illas 
               volu<lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>mus quibus libra iustitie suffragatur. <!--221.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e257">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
                / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e278">Li. 9. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e261">Aurum siquidem per bella 
               que<lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>rere nephas est: per maria periculum: per
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>falsitates opprobrium: in sua vero natura iustitia.
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>Honesta sunt lucra per que nemo leditur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>Bene queritur quod a nullis adhuc dominis
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>abrogatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e275">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e296">14. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e277">Commodum debet esse cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>modo. nam si mensuram equalitatis 
               exces<lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>serit vim sui nominis non habebt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e286">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e309">15. e.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e288">Illud tantum vere possumus lucrum dicere quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>constat diuina iudicia non punire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e296">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e321">Li. 11
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>e. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e298">Quid acquiri putatur vbi bona conscientia 
               per<lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>ditur: aut in qua parte possit homo 
               perfice<lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>re si innocentiam probatus fuerit amisisse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
                / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e338">Li. 12 e. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e312">Ultra omnes crudelitates est
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>diuitem velle fieri de exiguitate mendici.
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>Amentur honesta lucra: horreantur 
               dam<lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>nosa compendia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e322">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
                ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Rd1e354">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 46.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e326">Est id 
               tur<lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>pe lucrum quod detestatur honestas.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>Ferre solent damna crimine plena lucra.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
